BUOC 1: PHAN VUNG LAI O CUNG, TAO 40GB VUNG TRONG

BUOC 2: CAM USB CAI UBUNTU, VAO TRY UBUNTU

BUOC 3: VAO GPARTED, DELETE PHAN VUNG 40GB

BUOC 4: INSTALL UBUNTU, CHON "TRY SOMETHING ELSE"

BUOC 5: CHON FREE SPACES -> "+" -> SWAP AREA -> LOGICAL -> 17000MB -> OK

BUOC 6: CHON FREE SPACES -> "+" -> EXT4 -> PRIMARY -> "/" -> OK

BUOC 7: CHON WINDOW BOOT MANAGER -> OK

BUOC 8: INSTALL, XONG THI RESTART, RUT USB, VAO BOOT MANAGER, CHON UBUNTU 

BUOC 9: TAI DOCKER: LAM THEO HUONG DAN O DIGITALOCEAN

BUOC 10: CAI DRIVER CHO GPU:
	- AMD GPU: TU DONG CAI SAN
	- NVIDIA GPU: 
		ubuntu-drivers devices
		sudo ubuntu-drivers autoinstall
		
		sudo reboot       [QUAN TRONG!]

BUOC 11: CAI TOOLKIT CHO DOCKER
	- AMD GPU: CAI ROCM
	- NVIDIA GPU: NVIDIA CONTAINTER TOOLKIT

BUOC 12: DOWN FILE IMAGE:
	docker pull <Ten_image>
	
BUOC 13: xhost +local: docker

BUOC 14: LAY ID IMAGE:
	docker image ls
	
BUOC 15: ADD IMAGE VAO CONTAINER:
	- NVIDIA GPU:
		docker run --name it-car -it -p 11000:11000 --network="host" -e DISPLAY=$DISPLAY -v /tmp/.X11-unix:/tmp/.X11-unix --gpus all "imageid"
	- AMD GPU:
		docker run -it --device=/dev/kfd --device=/dev/dri --group-add video \
  -e DISPLAY=$DISPLAY -v /tmp/.X11-unix:/tmp/.X11-unix \
  --network=host \
  --name it-car 9 "imageid"
  
BUOC 16: CAI VS CODE VER 1.83.1, DOWN EXTENSION "DOCKER" VA "DEV CONTAINER"
 
BUOC 17: VAO DOCKER -> CONTAINER -> CHUOT PHAI -> START

BUOC 18: ATTACH VISUAL STUDIO CODE -> CHON WORKSPACE
  
  
